#GATK CallableLoci
#Adjustments to options needed for each run:
#input bam, -iinput_bam
#input bai, -iinput_bai
#output files prefix, -ioutput_prefix
#output path, --destination
#set region/chromosome, -L 
#maximum coverage threshold (dependent on platform-- 2x mean depth), -maxDepth

#Run for HG005 on 7/26/16 ran 29 min to 2 hr 11  min 
#looked at coverage depth for solid median DP for chr20 was 33 .  I am adjusting maxDepth= 66 for this data set. 
#There was no bam for MT so callable loci was not run for this chromosome
